Quadraturin 2D graphic engine
=============================

The project is suited to work in Eclipse SDK environment. Depends on "util" project. 

JOGL overview and links - http://download.java.net/media/jogl/builds/archive/jsr-231-1.1.0/jogl-1.1.0-windows-i586/Userguide.html

Debug
-----
* Use -ea -Dq.debug=true JVM param to enable debugging. 
	> F1 - toggle coordinate grid
	> F2 - toggle sensor radius
	> F3 - toggle bounding boxes
	> F4 - toggle force and velocity vectors

JVM params
----------
* Use -Dsun.awt.noerasebackground=true JVM parameter to disable flickering on aplication's frame resize.
* Use -Dsun.java2d.noddraw=true to disable DirectX for swing (prevent graphic artifacts outside of the GLCanvas).




